init.description:
To activate two factor authentication using time-based one-time passwords, scan the QR code with your authentication app. If you don't have one, we recommend either [Google Authenticator](https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/1066447) or [Authy](https://authy.com/).

{qr_code}

After scanning the code, enter the six digit code from your app to verify the setup. If you have problems scanning the QR code, do a manual setup with code **`{code}`**.
